  "text": "Due to the rapid development of modern industrial economy, the discharge of heavy metal sewage is becoming increasingly serious and poses a significant amount of threat to the environment and biological health. Heavy metals are highly toxic, non-degradable, bioaccumulative, and easy to enrich and transfer in the food chain. They pollute the agricultural products and food causing serious harm [CITATION_1] . In view of the heavy metal pollution, the development of a simple, rapid, and accurate MIF is of great significance to protect the environment of agricultural products, food quality, and safety.",
